Monday at Moe's  I am really at a loss for words. I had a bad experience at a particular location. I actually prefer Moe's over the competition. This particular franchise needs customer service, patience and learn how to be polite. Also a hourly bathroom cleaning checklist.. We got none of the above. I choose to eat elsewhere and while I waited for my partner to eat, I needed to use restroom While the language barrier is hard enough. The tone and level of frustration is easy to pick up. After the employee stared at me for 30 seconds she said it was out of order. I came back and and before me saying anything else. They yelled it again. I politely walked away got a piece of paper asked for a pen, when they replied, they don't have one. I found one in my bag and asked for their names. No one had a tag on. I told them it was for corporate, then they offered if I would like to use the men's. I said yes. Its a one person bathroom. When I opened the door, it looked like a horror show. Urine everywhere, tissue all over the toilet and ground. No towels or sanitizer anywhere in the store. I was appalled, disappointed and obviously disgusted. I respectly declined to use the facilities there.. The were rude about that too.  I don't want to have a bad taste in my when I think of Moe's. Please fix it. Remita.trowery@yahoo.com
